                <div1>
                    <div2>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0173a01"/>大齊東<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">平</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">郡</unclear>須昌縣□檀寺碑
                    </div2>
                    <div2>
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b01"/>夫旨理<note n="0173001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30966;＝淵【中研院】</note><app n="0173001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30966;</rdg></app>寂。凝然澄湛。百非不<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">能</unclear>非其非。千是無
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b02"/>以是其是。形言絕相。万像無能比其色。十<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">住</unclear>猶疑。
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b03"/>□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">凡</unclear>情之所觀□。自非應說教門。真□叵顯。是以
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b04"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">降</unclear>神閻浮。曜靈光於羅衛。<note n="0173002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30967;＝戒【中研院】</note><app n="0173002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">戒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30967;</rdg></app>風吹於大千。慈海流
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b05"/>於十域。慧鏡<note n="0173003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30620;＝照【中研院】</note><app n="0173003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">照</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30620;</rdg></app><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">愚</unclear>。若琉璃之現色影。魔道□心。有
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b06"/>緣皆益。攝影雙林。息障邁於千□□不疏體五住
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b07"/>之蹤。何能信矣。□佛弟子比丘法<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">慧</unclear>欲使<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">聖</unclear>教再
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b08"/>彰。神暉重朗。遠召□工。奉<note n="0173004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30369;＝剛【中研院】</note><app n="0173004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">剛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30369;</rdg></app>彫玉。<note n="0173005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30968;＝置【中研院】</note><app n="0173005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">置</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30968;</rdg></app>靈尊於上堪。
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b09"/>剟觀音經於下□。願使　皇道竄<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">興</unclear>。父師常<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">樂</unclear>。邑
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b10"/>儀諸人。龍華初會。法界有形。等成正覺。其頌曰。
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b11"/>真趣幽微。弗可言宣。大慈垂訓。以教流傳。初演鹿
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b12"/>菀。靈鷲陳章。摧魔伏道。如日<note n="0173006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30620;＝照【中研院】</note><app n="0173006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">照</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30620;</rdg></app>霜。敬<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">造</unclear>□形。<note n="0173007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30968;＝置【中研院】</note><app n="0173007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">置</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30968;</rdg></app>于
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b13"/>巖壑。刊經揚義。法流枯<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">涸</unclear>。
                           <lb ed="I" n="0173b14"/>大齊皇建元年庚辰□九月己酉朔三日辛亥造經碑
